## 7. QUY TẮC PRISMA

### 7.1. Schema conventions

```prisma
model Room {
  // PK: camelCase + "Id", autoincrement, @map("snake_case")
  roomId          Int       @id @default(autoincrement()) @map("room_id")

  // Fields: camelCase trong Prisma, snake_case trong DB
  roomName        String    @map("room_name") @db.VarChar(255)
  floor           Int?

  // Soft delete fields — BẮT BUỘC cho mọi model
  dataStatus      Int       @default(1) @map("data_status")
  createdStaffId  Int?      @map("created_staff_id")
  updatedStaffId  Int?      @map("updated_staff_id")
  deletedStaffId  Int?      @map("deleted_staff_id")
  createdAt       DateTime  @default(now()) @map("created_at")
  updatedAt       DateTime  @updatedAt @map("updated_at")
  deletedAt       DateTime? @map("deleted_at")

  // Relations — đặt cuối
  roomClass       RoomClass @relation(fields: [roomClassId], references: [roomClassId])
  roomClassId     Int       @map("room_class_id")

  // Table name: snake_case, số nhiều
  @@map("rooms")
}
```

### 7.2. Sau khi sửa schema:

```bash
pnpm prisma:generate      # Regenerate Prisma client
pnpm prisma:migrate        # Tạo migration mới
```

### 7.3. KHÔNG ĐƯỢC sửa file trong `node_modules/@prisma/client` — chúng là auto-generated

---

## 8. QUY TẮC ERROR HANDLING

### 8.1. Dùng NestJS built-in exceptions

```typescript
import {
  NotFoundException,
  BadRequestException,
  UnauthorizedException,
  ForbiddenException,
  ConflictException,
} from '@nestjs/common';

// ✅ ĐÚNG
throw new NotFoundException('Room not found');
throw new ConflictException('Room name already exists');

// ❌ SAI — KHÔNG throw Error thuần
throw new Error('Room not found');
```

### 8.2. Dùng constants cho error messages

```typescript
import { ERROR_MESSAGES } from '@common/constants/index';

throw new UnauthorizedException(ERROR_MESSAGES.UNAUTHORIZED);
```

